00:58:01.940 --> 00:58:04.087
You just get some dirty glass and give it to Mother,

00:58:04.112 --> 00:58:05.690
is not the way it is to be done.

00:58:05.715 --> 00:58:07.431
You see, you must understand after all you

00:58:07.456 --> 00:58:09.806
come from a country which has samskaras,

00:58:09.828 --> 00:58:12.596
which knows what is a puja, what is a holy person

00:58:12.621 --> 00:58:13.940
is and everything is.

00:58:13.953 --> 00:58:17.267
And then when you know that, you should understand

00:58:17.280 --> 00:58:19.217
that this is very important for that

00:58:19.221 --> 00:58:20.846
whatever is needed has to be done.

00:58:20.853 --> 00:58:23.115
If you have a photograph of a wrong person

00:58:24.148 --> 00:58:25.906
your, house will be ruined.

00:58:26.359 --> 00:58:28.440
Even [unclear sounds like ‘diamond’] you have seen it happens.

00:58:28.446 --> 00:58:31.012
If you have the photograph of a holy person,

00:58:31.480 --> 00:58:32.828
everything will be alright.

00:58:32.852 --> 00:58:35.696
It is for your good. I am not going to gain anything out of it.

00:58:35.696 --> 00:58:37.685
And photograph is not that expensive

00:58:37.710 --> 00:58:40.012
that you should think about. First we start, just have.

00:58:40.037 --> 00:58:42.375
It`s the minimum price, I think one Rupee.

00:58:42.400 --> 00:58:45.217
If you can afford it I`ll be happy. Thank you.